text: “thæcring than thanghlay nan sahrab brrda phu thi yakcn læa brrda phu thi khadsn læa brrda ceahnathi nı kar rwbrwm man læa brrda phu thi hawcı khxng phwk khea snithsnm læa nı kar thi thas læa brrda phu thi hnisin ln taw læa nı thang khx ngxallxh læa phu thi xyu nı rahwang deinthang thangni pen bayyati xan capen sung ma ca kxallxh læa xallxh nan pen phuthrng rxbru phuthrng pricha yan”
